text: Kaznatash () is a rural locality (a village) in Novosubayevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 13 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 3 km from Novy Subay. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Kaznatash
